'''Corran''' was the son of a hydroponic [[Farmer/Legends|farmer]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Séléann]]. His [[Corran's father|father]] was a supporter of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], even when the planetary [[Governor/Legends|governor]] declared allegiance with the Empire. Corran did not wish to leave his life on his homeworld, and he enjoyed hunting [[Tian-Ki]] with his [[Blaster rifle/Legends|blaster rifle]].

